update node with these commands

**run the node:**  

```screen -x nubit```

**close the current node with:**
ctl + c

**update it by :**

```curl -sL1 https://nubit.sh/ | bash```

**check the seed phrase:**  

```
cd
cd nubit-node
nano mnemonic.txt
```

if it is the same then your node is updated.

**check your uptime :**
```
$HOME/nubit-node/bin/nubit das sampling-stats --node.store $HOME/.nubit-light-nubit-alphatestnet-1
```


